s made from a single piece of machined aluminium  the whole thing is polished first to a mirror finish and then is very finely textured except for the apple logo the chamfers smoothedoff edges are cut with diamondtipped cutters the cutters dont usually last very long so we had to figure out a way of massmanufacturing longlasting ones the camera cover is sapphire crystal look at the details around the simcard slot its extraordinary on september   apple introduced the iphone  alongside the iphone  plus that both have screen sizes over inches one year later apple introduced the iphone s and iphone s plus which introduced a new technology called d touch including an increase of the rear camera to  mp and the facetime camera to  mp on march   apple introduced the iphone se that has a inch size last used with the s and has the same internal hardware as the s iphone  and iphone  plus were introduced on september   on september   apple introduced the iphone  and the iphone  plus which feature improved system and graphics performance add water resistance a new rear dualcamera system on the  plus model and controversially remove the  mm headphone jack in july  apple announced that one billion iphones had been sold ipad main article ipad ipad air  in gold on january   apple introduced their muchanticipated media tablet the ipad it offers multitouch interaction with multimedia formats including newspapers ebooks photos videos music word processing documents video games and most existing iphone apps using a inch screen it also includes a mobile version of safari for web browsing as well as access to the app store itunes library ibookstore contacts and notes content is downloadable via wifi and optional g service or synced through the users computer att was initially the sole us provider of g wireless access for the ipad on march   apple introduced the ipad  which had a faster processor and a camera on the front and back it also added support for optional g service provided by ve