ation a henkel company effective september   henkel acquired the us laundry and home care company the sun products corporation with a transaction volume of around  billion euros the acquisition is the second largest in henkel’s history the acquisition is a stepchange for the business with henkel reaching the no  position in the north american laundry care market sun products’ portfolio includes wellknown and successful brands such as all and sun detergent and snuggle fabric conditioner and the company serves as a manufacturer and marketing partner to many of north america’s leading retailers with a store brand portfolio of laundry and dish care products careers explore open positions in connecticut material testing technician rocky hill ct assistant brand manager  beauty stamford senior purchasing agent  industrial packaging rocky hill ct manager shopper marketing stamford srregulatory specialist – laundry and home care trumbull load more join the henkel team and see where your career can take you find out more about our exciting job opportunities in connecticut brands top brand all trusted stain removal on the toughest kid stains more info alllaundrycom snuggle more info sun laundry  dish more info wwwsundetergentcom sunlight more info surf more info wwwsurfdetergentcom further information safety data sheets  ingredient disclosures browse our database to find the sds and ingredient disclosures you are looking for locations discover all henkel locations in north america